# Conventions and Patterns

Imports and aliases
- Path alias: `@/*` → repo root (see `tsconfig.json`)
- shadcn aliases in `components.json` (for reference): `components`, `ui`, `lib`, `hooks`

Components
- Server by default; add `"use client"` for interactive (e.g., `components/ui/avatar.tsx`, `components/ui/sheet.tsx`)
- UI primitives wrap Radix components; style via `cva` variants and `cn`
- Icons: prefer `lucide-react` or `@icons-pack/react-simple-icons`

Styling
- Tailwind v4 with `@tailwindcss/postcss`; import in `app/globals.css`
- Theme via CSS variables (OKLCH) on `:root` and `.dark`; dark variant via `@custom-variant dark`
- Base styles use `@layer base` and Tailwind tokens (e.g., `bg-background`, `text-foreground`)

Routing and layout
- App Router; global layout adds a fixed bottom `Navbar`
- Sections on home page use IDs: `#introduction`, `#experience`

Assets and media
- Static files under `public/`; reference with `/images/...` and `next/image`

Quality
- ESLint flat config extends Next’s core-web-vitals + TypeScript
- TypeScript strict enabled; `moduleResolution: bundler`
